---
title: Bengali Halloumi & Roast Pumpkin Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Dive into the vibrant flavours of this meat-free curry! Golden, seared halloumi and sweet roasted veggies get a thick coating of the luscious Bengali coconut sauce. Served with fragrant garlic rice and a sprinkle of fresh coriander, it’s a bowl of comfort—perfect for curry night!
